desc: Treatment for dry eyes providing instant relief and all day comfort. Australian Optometrists developed a natural remedy using Manuka Honey and Tea Tree oil ingredients to relieve the symptoms of dry eyes. Optimel Manuka Honey Eye Drops, Blephadex Wipes and Hylo Forte Drops help to heal dry eyes and provide relief.
